</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Capcom《Exoprimal》     5 人組隊大戰恐龍大軍</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/10/capcom-announces-dinosaur-themed-team-based-action-game-exoprimal-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-and-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=capcom-announces-dinosaur-themed-team-based-action-game-exoprimal-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-xbox-one-and-pc</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 10 Mar 2022 09:30:21 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[capcom]]></category><category><![CDATA[Exopriaml]]></category><category><![CDATA[State of Play]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1090153</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Capcom 於今日上午舉辦的「State of Play」直播節目中，宣佈將於 2023 年推出的原創新作《 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Capcom 於今日上午舉辦的「State of Play」直播節目中，宣佈將於 2023 年推出的原創新作《Exoprimal》，將登陸 PC、PS5、PS4、Xbox Series X|S 及 Xbox One。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967-694x438.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967-694x438.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967-1280x808.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967-768x485.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967-1536x970.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C3EE8112-53AA-43EC-BC10-1DD70EE9B967.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/C5CA38E1-C108-4691-9439-7C434F6F87C4-694x388.jpeg" alt