</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Square《Valkyrie Elysium》     女神戰記系列最新 ARPG</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/10/square-enix-announces-action-rpg-valkyrie-elysium-for-ps5-ps4-and-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=square-enix-announces-action-rpg-valkyrie-elysium-for-ps5-ps4-and-pc</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 10 Mar 2022 08:28:08 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS4]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS5]]></category><category><![CDATA[square enix]]></category><category><![CDATA[steam]]></category><category><![CDATA[女神，極樂淨土]]></category><category><![CDATA[女神戰記]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1090084</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>SQUARE ENIX 於今日上午舉辦的「State of Play」直播節目中，宣佈將於 2022 年在 P [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">SQUARE ENIX 於今日上午舉辦的「State of Play」直播節目中，宣佈將於 2022 年在 PS5、PS4 與 Steam 平台推出動作角色扮演遊戲新作《Valkyrie Elysium（女神，極樂淨土，暫譯）》。遊戲以北歐神話為背景，首度採用動作角色扮演遊戲設計，更可支援繁體中文。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1-694x364.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1-694x364.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1-1280x671.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1-768x403.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1-1536x805.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/957CF003-6261-44D1-9BBE-6B00279FF3F1.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090086" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-694x385.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-694x385.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-1280x711.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-768x426.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-1536x853.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616-2048x1137.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/797DCD61-7E62-4F0B-841B-CE34F521B616.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1090087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-694x383.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="383" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-694x383.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-1280x707.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-768x424.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-1536x848.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82-2048x1131.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1C6352A0-4E76-496E-B035-9EC29E8B8B82.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Valkyrie Elysium》為《女神戰記》系列最新作品，故事以北歐神話展開，由於末日的宿命「諸神黃昏」，世界曾瀕臨毀滅的危機。主宰萬物的主神，用所剩無幾的力量創造「救贖的使徒」，並將世界的命運託付於全新的「女武神」。遊戲採用高品質圖像描繪嶄新的《女神戰記》世界，並加入由原班底音樂家櫻庭統譜寫的配樂。承襲系列一貫的動作角色扮演玩法，收錄熟悉的必殺技與連段系統，並進化為更具立體感與速度感的戰鬥。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" c